data.description: One owner home, very nice 4 bdrm, 2bath, 2 living area. Large kitchen, tons of cabinets, gas range. NNew flooring throughout, roof, paint, some windows, fixtures all added in 2019 per seller. Finished basement would be a great playroom, office or gym. Central heat & air, fenced back yard extra long driveway to park additional cars or add a carport or garage. Each room is spacious and has wonderful closet space. Plenty of room for a large family or a couple making the additional rooms for guest or craft room You will love the possibilities.
